# IT Infrastructure Stabilization Post Go-Live

The first 90 days after commissioning are critical.

## Common Challenges
- Performance bottlenecks
- User errors and training gaps
- Workflow misalignment
- Vendor dependency issues

## Stabilization Actions
- Daily system health monitoring
- User feedback loops
- Incremental optimization
- Vendor accountability tracking

